    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WARNING: THIS GAME WILL INFURIATE YOU</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Grapple Hook Gameplay, Swing from object to object to try and reach the top of the world before time runs out. Use your momentum to build speed and achieve higher jumps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/7b7a43d74d728ebf7f4c3668ef5d9de0.poster.avif?t=1752536431\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/7b7a43d74d728ebf7f4c3668ef5d9de0.webm?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/7b7a43d74d728ebf7f4c3668ef5d9de0.mp4?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Collect Coins, Chalices, and Chests</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/64778f09c120a4884cd2d726846388b8.poster.avif?t=1752536431\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/64778f09c120a4884cd2d726846388b8.webm?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/64778f09c120a4884cd2d726846388b8.mp4?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use Collected Items To Purchase Upgrades like a Hover Pack! (And many other things)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/b23b14b8397e0c114efbc1d79fb93a4f.poster.avif?t=1752536431\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/b23b14b8397e0c114efbc1d79fb93a4f.webm?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/b23b14b8397e0c114efbc1d79fb93a4f.mp4?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Swing Gameplay With A Swing Jazz Soundtrack &amp; PACHINKO, spend your hard earned money on gambling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/5f1c3d735ce3628971e2ff720fafaef6.poster.avif?t=1752536431\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/5f1c3d735ce3628971e2ff720fafaef6.webm?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/5f1c3d735ce3628971e2ff720fafaef6.mp4?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Different Dimensions to SPEEDRUN, Reach the end of the game before time runs out. Try to go as fast as you can through the 6 dimensions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/505877c04e9efcb2a7342cc41bba03d4.poster.avif?t=1752536431\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/505877c04e9efcb2a7342cc41bba03d4.webm?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404970/extras/505877c04e9efcb2a7342cc41bba03d4.mp4?t=1752536431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3 Different Endings Based On What You Want Most</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIND YOUR DIMENSION BEFORE TIME RUNS OUT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been selected to participate in an experiment where you can make your wildest dream come true! You can be taken to a dimension where you are the most wealthy, the most powerful, or the most happy. The only catch is you can't stop once you've started - and you have to reach the end before the time runs out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you reach your chosen dimension, do you really think it will be everything you've ever wanted?</p>",
